    <string name="main_custom_theme_description">Each HEX box previews its own color. Background controls the main page and drawer base; Panel controls general cards, search fields, drawer headers, and dialog panels; App bar controls top bars; Text controls primary labels/icons; Secondary text controls metadata/hints; Outline controls borders/dividers; Selected controls general selected highlights; File type button controls the unselected All/General/Archive/PDF/EPUB/Word/IMG filter chips; Selected file type button controls the selected filter chip; Reading theme card controls the card rows in the reading-theme list; Shortcut box controls the icon boxes in the navigation drawer shortcuts; Drawer action icon controls the File Open/Bookmarks/Settings icons at the bottom of the drawer. Use HEX or the RGB sliders below each box.</string>
